articles.author: Jake Boxall-Legge
articles.title: F1 Miami GP: Verstappen storms to victory from ninth on the grid - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Max Verstappen overcame Sergio Perez in a strategic battle between Red Bulls in Formula 1's Miami Grand Prix, overtaking his team-mate on the 48th lap.
